1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,420
A fake couple?

2
00:00:02,420 --> 00:00:06,210
With Yuki's looks,
girls just won't leave him alone, right?

3
00:00:06,210 --> 00:00:10,550
So to avoid
all that unwanted attention...

4
00:00:10,550 --> 00:00:12,890
we're just pretending to be a couple.

5
00:00:12,890 --> 00:00:15,020
Unwanted attention...?

6
00:00:15,470 --> 00:00:18,940
I'm only telling you this
because you seem trustworthy.

7
00:00:18,940 --> 00:00:22,310
The truth is, I'm into women.

8
00:00:22,310 --> 00:00:23,400
Huh?

9
00:00:23,400 --> 00:00:28,450
But it's a hassle explaining it
every time I have to turn a guy down.

10
00:00:28,450 --> 00:00:32,870
So we have this arrangement
as a fake couple. It works out for both of us.

11
00:00:32,870 --> 00:00:35,660
There are no romantic feelings involved.

12
00:00:35,660 --> 00:00:39,410
But what's Yuki's reason for doing this?

13
00:00:39,410 --> 00:00:42,790
As for Yuki,
you should probably ask him yourself.

14
00:00:42,790 --> 00:00:45,800
It's not my place to say.

15
00:00:45,800 --> 00:00:50,010
Yeah, I guess you're right.

16
00:00:50,010 --> 00:00:53,220
Natsu-san,
you really are someone I can trust.

17
00:00:53,220 --> 00:00:55,720
You bet!

18
00:00:55,720 --> 00:00:57,060
Yuki is too.

19
00:00:57,060 --> 00:01:00,480
That's true. Word never got out
that I was dumped.

20
00:01:00,480 --> 00:01:01,690
See?

21
00:01:01,690 --> 00:01:05,770
Well, I've sobered up a bit.
I should get going.

22
00:01:05,770 --> 00:01:07,530
Oh, it's late.
Let me walk you home.

23
00:01:07,530 --> 00:01:09,860
It's okay. My girlfriend's here to pick me up.

24
00:01:09,860 --> 00:01:11,450
Makoto-kun, you should just stay the night.

25
00:01:12,360 --> 00:01:15,080
Take care of Yuki for me. Bye!

26
00:01:15,530 --> 00:01:17,660
(A fake couple...)

27
00:01:17,660 --> 00:01:19,580
(But why would Yuki...)

28
00:01:19,580 --> 00:01:24,000
Yuki, you'll catch a cold sleeping out here.
Why don't you go to bed?

29
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,540
Mmm.

30
00:01:25,540 --> 00:01:28,420
I'm not strong enough
to carry you to your room.

31
00:01:28,420 --> 00:01:32,010
- Let's sleep together...
- Hey! Mmph!
